[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_0",
    "text": "4.利用经纬网定位",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11808461180846118,
      0.14807502467917077,
      0.3449558344955834,
      0.16847647252385653
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_1",
    "text": "0)经纬网的合义：在地球仪或地图上经线和纬线相互交织所构成的网络。 (经纬网的作用：确定地球表面某一点的位置。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1487680148768015,
      0.17703191839420862,
      0.9298000929800093,
      0.23231326094109905
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_2",
    "text": "地球的运动",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12087401208740121,
      0.27311615663047056,
      0.2612738261273826,
      0.2935176044751563
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_3",
    "text": "1.地球的自转",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12738261273826126,
      0.30536360644948995,
      0.28172942817294283,
      0.3251069430733794
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_4",
    "text": "(1)含义：地球绕着地轴不停地旋转。 (2)方向：自而向东： (3)周期：一天(约为24小时). (4)产生的现象：昼夜更替、地方时差",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15527661552766156,
      0.33497861138532414,
      0.5550906555090656,
      0.4573872984534386
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_5",
    "text": "2、地球的公转",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12645281264528127,
      0.491609081934847,
      0.29660622966062294,
      0.512668641000329
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_6",
    "text": "(1)含义：地球围绕太阳不停地旋转 (2)方向：自而向东。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16457461645746166,
      0.5225403093122738,
      0.5653184565318456,
      0.5811122079631458
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_7",
    "text": "(3)周期：一年(约为365天).",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16922361692236168,
      0.5863770977295163,
      0.44537424453742447,
      0.6074366567949984
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_8",
    "text": "(4)特点：地球公转的轨道平面与地轴的央角是66.5)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17201301720130172,
      0.6153339914445541,
      0.7317526731752673,
      0.644290885159592
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_9",
    "text": "(5)产生的现象：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17108321710832172,
      0.6495557749259625,
      0.3356578335657834,
      0.6706153339914446
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_10",
    "text": "①太阳直射点在南北回归线之间来回移动；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.200836820083682,
      0.6798288910825929,
      0.6369130636913064,
      0.7054952286936492
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_11",
    "text": "②同一地点、太阳高度角的变化：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20269642026964202,
      0.7107601184600197,
      0.5244072524407253,
      0.7370845672918723
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_12",
    "text": "③ 同一地点.昼夜长短的变氏",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20269642026964202,
      0.7423494570582428,
      0.5058112505811251,
      0.7680157946692991
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_13",
    "text": "④同一地点，不同季节太阳光热不同，即春夏秋冬四军的形成。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.19711761971176198,
      0.771964461994077,
      0.807996280799628,
      0.7982889108259296
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_14",
    "text": "(6)二分二至：春分日（6日21日前后)、夏至日（6日22日前后)、秋分日(9日23日前 后)、冬至日((2日22日前后)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12273361227336123,
      0.8028956893715038,
      0.9474662947466295,
      0.8601513655807832
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_8_15",
    "text": "(7) 四季的划分(以北半球为例，南半球正相反)：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
